disk_enables: mask of enabled disks in this layout

Status: Adaptor Status, 0 for disabled, 1 for enabled
bIPV4_Address: The Ipv4 address assigned to the Network interface. If not available, all bytes are set to zero.
bMAC_Address: The Media Access Control (MAC) Address of the Network interface in the PC that is to be connected to the vehicle.

chksum: checksum to protect settings structure (don't want corrupt voltage settings)
mode: no poc, generated supply, serializer passthrough

gPTPportRole: the 5th port is used for SAM
portEnable: the 5th port is used for SAM

Reserved: may be expanded in future revisions

state: state of formatting (not started, writing file system, formatting, writing VSAs, finished)

selected_network: not supported yet - default to HSCAN
